---

<section class="dilemma-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-5">
      <h2 class="h1 text-white">The Startup Engineering Dilemma</h2>
      <p class="text-white opacity-70 max-width-600 mx-auto">Why founders waste time and capital on building development teams from scratch.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="dilemma-card">
          <div class="text-primary mb-3">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#52CEC7" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"></line>
              <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="h4 text-white mb-2">High Cost of Senior Hires</h3>
          <p class="text-white opacity-70 mb-0">Hiring a backend dev, a frontend dev, a designer, and a DevOps engineer costs upwards of £25,000/mo in salaries alone, excluding recruitment fees.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="dilemma-card">
          <div class="text-primary mb-3">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#52CEC7" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="h4 text-white mb-2">Slow Time to Market</h3>
          <p class="text-white opacity-70 mb-0">Recruiting, onboarding, and coordinating a new developer team takes 3 to 6 months. Your competitors are moving while you are still hiring.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="dilemma-card">
          <div class="text-primary mb-3">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#52CEC7" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle>
              <path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 1 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 1 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="h4 text-white mb-2">DevOps & AI Complexities</h3>
          <p class="text-white opacity-70 mb-0">Getting security parameters, CI/CD automated deployment, and scalable LLM/AI integrations right requires specialized knowledge that general devs lack.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
